{
  "texts": [
    "Once the edge lists are constructed, they are serialized in a JSON file.",
    "Ontology alignment.",
    "Foundry ontologies were selected because they represent canonical knowledge and exist for nearly all scales of biological organization 78.",
    "PKT-KG assumes that every KG is logically grounded 79 in one or more OBO Foundry ontologies.",
    "This feature leverages OWLTools to merge the ontologies into a single integrated core ontology."
  ]
}